OL,3,CMurderer dies at Parc Prison as
OL,4,Cfatalities reach nine in two months
OL,6,FTwo inmates have died at Bridgend's
OL,7,FParc Prison, bringing the total
OL,8,Ffatalities to nine in two months.
OL,10,FA HMP Parc spokesperson confirmed the
OL,11,Fdeaths of 73-year-old David Maggs and
OL,12,F19-year-old Michael Horton on Tuesday,
OL,13,F7 May.
OL,15,FTheir families and next of kin have
OL,16,Fbeen informed.
OL,18,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,19,F"Their deaths were unrelated. Family
OL,20,FLiason Officers are supporting the
OL,21,Ffamilies.
