OL,6,F"As with all deaths in custody, these
OL,7,Fwill be investigated by the Prisons
OL,8,Fand Probation Ombudsman."
OL,10,FFormer accountant Mr Maggs was
OL,11,Fconvicted of the murder of his wife,
OL,12,FLinda Maggs, whom he stabbed to death
OL,13,Fat their home in Pontypool in February
OL,14,F2021. She was 74.
OL,16,FSouth Wales police were called to Parc
OL,17,FPrison just after midnight on Tuesday
OL,18,Ffollowing reports of two "sudden
OL,19,Fdeaths."
