OL,7,Finvestigations are continuing into the
OL,8,Fcircumstances surrounding the deaths,
OL,9,Fwhich, they say, "are not believed to
OL,10,Fbe suspicious."
OL,12,F"It will be for HM Coroner to give a
OL,13,Fdetermination on the cause of death",
OL,14,Fthe police statement concluded.
