OL,6,F"Two of these deaths sadly occurred on
OL,7,F7 May 2024. As I said in March, I am
OL,8,Fsaddened by this high number, but I am
OL,9,Fnow also concerned by the increase."
OL,11,FHe continued: "Our investigations into
OL,12,Fthe two recent deaths have begun, and
OL,13,Fwe will publish our final
OL,14,Finvestigation reports on our website
OL,15,Fonce the inquests conclude. I offer my
OL,16,Fcondolences to the family and friends
OL,17,Fof those affected."
