OL,6,FIt comes after an ITV Cymru Wales in
OL,7,Fwhich the jail was described as a "war
OL,8,Fzone", with prison officers paid to
OL,9,Fbring in drugs.
OL,11,FAn HMP Parc spokesperson has rejected
OL,12,Fthe inmate's claims, saying there are
OL,13,Fstrategies in place to root out drugs
OL,14,Fand contraband, and adding that the
OL,15,F"vast majority of their staff are
OL,16,Fhonest and hardworking."
OL,18,Fat Parc between 27 February and 19
OL,19,FMarch - police believe four of the
OL,20,Fdeaths were drug-related.
